properties.Name: AminoAcidFunction
properties.Description:
A specific physical function that may be associated with an amino acid, protein, gene etc.

Ex:
- lipid transport
- excitatory neurotransmitters
- inhibitory neurotransmitters
- connective tissue generation
- precursor of nitric oxide
